            "title": "半日收市｜港股半日升154點  光伏股及生科股飆",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股半日升154點，光伏股狂飆，生科、機器人股及晶片股俱炒上，網上醫療股受壓。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數半日升154點或0.62%，報25212，今早競價時段開報25136，升77點或0.31%，最低報25090，升32點或0.13%，為半日低位，其後股價向上，高見25244，升186點或0.74%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"協鑫科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/03800-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"協鑫科技官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/03800-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">協鑫科技官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"中國生物製藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國生物製藥官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"協鑫科技官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/03800-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">協鑫科技官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國生物製藥官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數半日升52點或0.59%，報8989點，今早開報5602，升23點或0.42% ;</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數半日升45點或0.82%，報5624點，今早開報8960，升22點或0.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日報25173，升200點或0.8%，科指期貨報5634點，升57點或1.02%，高水9 點; 國指期貨報8968點，升56點或0.63%，低水22點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1246.29億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">光伏相關股份揚升，協鑫科技(03800)曾高見1.47元，彈12.2%，半日升10.69%，報1.45元，入20大成交額，協鑫新能源(00451)飆13.33%，報1.02元。信義光能(00968)升5.22%，報3.63元，為表現最佳藍籌股；同系的信義玻璃(00868)升3.05%，報8.42元；信義能源(03868)飛升10.32%，報1.39元; 福萊特玻璃(06865)抽高7.69%，報12.05元 ; 新特能源(01799)飆12.67%，報8.54元。國家工信部、市場監督管理總局稱依法治理光伏等產品低價競爭、引導地方有序佈局光伏、鋰電池產業。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"協鑫科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/03800-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"協鑫科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/03800-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">協鑫科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生科股及藥股普遍造好，中國生物製藥(01177)升5.24%，報8.83元 ; 翰森製藥(03692)升3.49%，報36.74% ; 石藥(01093)升2.86%，報11.14元 ; 藥明生物(02269)升4.65%，報36.92元 ; 藥明康德(02359)升3.12%，報112.4元 ; 藥明合聯(02268)升2.21%，報64.55元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國生物製藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國生物製藥官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">網上醫療股受壓，京東健康(06618)跌2.48%，報62.8元 ; 阿里健康(00241)跌1.23%，報6.41元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">機器人股炒上，地平線機器人(09660)飆7.79%，報9.69元 ; 優必選(09880)升2.54%，報105.1元，成交入20大  </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股受捧，中芯(00981)升4.02%，報58.25元，成交居第二位 ; 華虹半導體(01347)升2.58%，報46.86元，成交入20大。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
