        },
        {
            "title": "港股開升77點   運動服股升  騰訊小米升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數競價時段開報25136，升77點或0.31% ; 恒生科技指數開報5602，升23點或0.42% ; 恒生國企指數開報8960，升22點或0.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交26.84億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"李寧官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/02331-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"李寧官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/02331-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">李寧官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)開升1.18%，報599.5元 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)跌1%，報128.5元 ; 小米(01810)升1.03%，報54元 ; 攜程(09961)升1.34%，報569.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">運動服股升，安踏(02020)升1.92%，報95.5 ; 李寧(02331)升3.5%，報19.24元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯(00981)升1.43%，報56.8元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)升0.9%，報100.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">復星國際(00656)無升，報5.27元，附屬公司售葡萄牙醫療集團部份股份。</p>\n</div>",
